reviewText:
Early Access Review

In fact one person is working on this game. Although this game looks nice.

Good points:
Remarkably drawn pixel sprites, rooms and outdoor locations looks atmospheric;
Interesting and diverse skills in each class;
Many equipment and potions;
The ability to fine-tune the interface;
Various secrets;
Quests and story line;
Not bad bosses and a variety of enemies;
One screen" multiplayer with gamepad support;
Fast feedback with developer.And many other pleasant things.

Bad points:
Development of the game takes time
